doc.after: The Aer Lingus head office is located on the grounds of Dublin Airport in Fingal, County Dublin.[75] The HOB Site,[76] the 9.9-acre (4.0Â ha) head office site includes the head office building, the services annexe, the Iolar House,[77] the Mock-Up Building, the ALSAA swimming pool, and various smaller structures and buildings.[76] The Head Office Building houses the corporate head office of Aer Lingus and its subsidiaries, and many administrative functions, employees, and car parking spaces, are located in this building. The Iolar House and Mock-Up Building house training facilities for Aer Lingus crew and office space.[76]
